{"tid":1204194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奏軍樂，振士氣，你我能參與！","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T18:35:33.000Z","uid":188428,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f321c705014a5b240fa6b01b9f50bbc64ce7b247","tid":1204194,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"軍心，是要用激昂的軍樂去鞏固的。<br />\n就好似扒龍舟咁，要令一team人上下一條心，<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130623/photo/0623-00176-023h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130623%2Fphoto%2F0623-00176-023h1.jpg&h=865a4bcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最有效嘅方法，就係<span style=\"color: red;\">演奏軍樂</span>。</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n一部正式嘅軍隊都有Marching Band.<br />\n千祈唔好睇小，軍樂絕對係重要嘅一環。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.defense.gov/2016/Mar/11/2001479042/-1/-1/0/160310-Z-SV144-024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.defense.gov%2F2016%2FMar%2F11%2F2001479042%2F-1%2F-1%2F0%2F160310-Z-SV144-024.JPG&h=860a3bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>你可以做到啲咩？</strong></ins></span><br />\n善用物品，你也可以參與演奏軍樂，體驗一下激昂的氣勢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OcwLe4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOcwLe4t.jpg&h=1123639c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hm-whistle.com/html-cn/image/1-znTmyEeUjJRq-1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hm-whistle.com%2Fhtml-cn%2Fimage%2F1-znTmyEeUjJRq-1-1.jpg&h=1761cf6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://nationwideradiojm.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Vuvuzela-630x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnationwideradiojm.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FVuvuzela-630x400.jpg&h=0d1d4e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1ezgBa.vMR1JjSZPcq6A1tFXaj/Rubber-Screaming-Chicken-Squawking-Shrilling-Fun-Novelty-Squeeze-Vent-Chicken-prank-Anti-stress-Toys-as-Gifts.jpg_640x640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fae01.alicdn.com%2Fkf%2FHTB1ezgBa.vMR1JjSZPcq6A1tFXaj%2FRubber-Screaming-Chicken-Squawking-Shrilling-Fun-Novelty-Squeeze-Vent-Chicken-prank-Anti-stress-Toys-as-Gifts.jpg_640x640.jpg&h=c0c0e287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.12早已經有人會玩喇，仲唔趕緊時機，一齊參與？！<br />\n奏軍樂，振士氣，你我能參與！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ffdc1f825fc659ee122ed2b3b7c38f0595575a","tid":1204194,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"吹小號得唔得"},{"pid":"823bf6bce12444dae668886218cb79893d502038","tid":1204194,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7ffdc1f825fc659ee122ed2b3b7c38f0595575a","tid":1204194,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"吹小號得唔得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"of course,<br />\n捨得帶出嚟就ok la!"},{"pid":"7734be011b034e0ee7e85ed62cf91f365ded8327","tid":1204194,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"823bf6bce12444dae668886218cb79893d502038","tid":1204194,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7ffdc1f825fc659ee122ed2b3b7c38f0595575a","tid":1204194,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"吹小號得唔得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"of course,<br />\n捨得帶出嚟就ok la!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"幾百蚊既膠野"},{"pid":"957f474f8d8da937e16cdeb33fa59cc59166522a","tid":1204194,"uid"